## Problem 1 — All Permutations of a String

**Question:** given `"abc"`, print all possible arrangements.

```
output: ["abc", "acb", "bac", "bca", "cab", "cba"]
```

**How to think about it:**

```
position 0 can be: a, b, or c
  if position 0 = a:
    position 1 can be: b or c
      if position 1 = b:
        position 2 must be: c → "abc" ✓
      if position 1 = c:
        position 2 must be: b → "acb" ✓
  if position 0 = b:
    position 1 can be: a or c
      ...and so on
```

```java
public List<String> permutations(String s) {
    List<String> result = new ArrayList<>();
    boolean[] used = new boolean[s.length()]; // tracks which chars are used
    backtrack(s, used, new StringBuilder(), result);
    return result;
}

private void backtrack(String s, boolean[] used,
                       StringBuilder current, List<String> result) {

    // BASE CASE — current has all characters
    if (current.length() == s.length()) {
        result.add(current.toString()); // copy and save
        return;
    }

    // EXPLORE — try every character
    for (int i = 0; i < s.length(); i++) {

        if (used[i]) continue; // already in current path — skip

        // 1. MAKE the choice
        used[i] = true;
        current.append(s.charAt(i));

        // 2. RECURSE
        backtrack(s, used, current, result);

        // 3. UNDO — backtrack
        used[i] = false;
        current.deleteCharAt(current.length() - 1);
    }
}
```

**Trace on `"abc"`:**

```
start: current=""  used=[F,F,F]

try i=0 ('a'): current="a"  used=[T,F,F]
  try i=1 ('b'): current="ab"  used=[T,T,F]
    try i=2 ('c'): current="abc"  used=[T,T,T]
      length==3 → add "abc" ✓
    undo i=2: current="ab"  used=[T,T,F]
  undo i=1: current="a"  used=[T,F,F]
  try i=2 ('c'): current="ac"  used=[T,F,T]
    try i=1 ('b'): current="acb"  used=[T,T,T]
      length==3 → add "acb" ✓
    undo i=1: current="ac"  used=[T,F,T]
  undo i=2: current="a"  used=[T,F,F]
undo i=0: current=""  used=[F,F,F]

try i=1 ('b'): current="b" ... → "bac", "bca"
try i=2 ('c'): current="c" ... → "cab", "cba"

result = ["abc", "acb", "bac", "bca", "cab", "cba"] ✅
```

